    <h2>Our History</h2>
    <p>Founded in 2023, Christian Alms Outreach emerged from a simple observation: while technology was revolutionizing every aspect of modern life, charitable organizations were often left behind. A group of Christian technologists, theologians, and charity workers came together to bridge this gap.</p>
    
    <p>What started as a small pilot program using basic algorithms to optimize food distribution has grown into a comprehensive platform that serves thousands of families across multiple states. Our success has proven that faith-based organizations can be at the forefront of technological innovation while maintaining their spiritual mission.</p>
    
